\begin_layout Standard
- For parameters to maximize: score += normalized_value 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
- For parameters to minimize: score -= normalized_value
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This heuristic balances waste reduction with other desirable meal qualities.
\end_layout

